What we need now that i come to think of it is a side style chain, since the side area was enlarged (if i remember corectly) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kethryndc>Kethryn DC</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 193<br> <font color=#000000>(6/4/03 4:30 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=104.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where do we go from 1.62?</span><hr size=1> The problems are:<br>
<br>
Aurora Borealis no longer has any effect other then the lame cold proc.<br>
<br>
And<br>
<br>
Our bleed damages did not get the same adjustment as the other light tanks.  So oh joy, for the 7! bleed damage.<br>
<br>
Also,<br>
<br>
they changed the snared effects (hinder on atrophy) to break with damage so if you run the chain you break it anyway.<br>
<br>
We have no direct effect styles.  Everyone requires a chain or in many instances a positional/reactionary off of a chain. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=noltmier>Noltmier</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Initiate</span><br>  Posts: 4<br> <font color=#000000>(6/4/03 6:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=104.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where do we go from 1.62?</span><hr size=1> You sure we didn't get the adjustment for bleed?  I only recently became 44, so I haven't used Icy Brilliance too much, but last night I noticed that the bleed started at 9, not at 7 as I had heard it did.  If I'm wrong and it started with 9 dmg before let me know. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#ffffff><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=kethryndc>Kethryn DC</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Seasoned Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 196<br> <font color=#000000>(6/4/03 7:02 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub79.ezboard.com/flighttanksofdaocfrm3.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=104.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Where do we go from 1.62?</span><hr size=1> Yes it starts at 9 but the new bleeds are starting at 40 and vary by resists the mobs in spind are very overconned (Oj there are like yellow/blue in SI and DF).   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#c0c0c0><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub79.ezboard.com/blighttanksofdaoc.showUserPublicProfile?gid=connorrowynsun>Connor Rowynsun</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 69<br> <font 